# Input
```css
/* should generate diagnostics */

/* accent-color is limited (not even newly available) */
a { accent-color: bar; }

/* view-transition at-rule is not yet newly available */
@view-transition { navigation: auto; }

/* device-posture media condition is not newly available */
@media (device-posture: folded) { a { color: red; } }

```

